## Kinertic Media Arts — environment variables
#
# This is a Vite project. Only variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed
# to browser code via `import.meta.env.*`.
#
# Note: as of the current codebase state, the frontend does not reference
# any env vars yet. Keep secrets server-side.

# Canonical site URL (used for link generation in future integrations)
VITE_SITE_URL=https://kinerticmedia.com

# Google Analytics Measurement ID (optional; example only)
VITE_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Contact form behavior (example placeholders)
# Keep email/API keys server-side; these are placeholders until a backend exists.
CONTACT_EMAIL=kinerticmedia97@gmail.com
CONTACT_FROM=noreply@kinerticmediaarts.com

# Example only — do NOT store real API keys in client-exposed env vars.
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxx
